title: Which Teams Did Zaza Pachulia Play For | StatMuse
snippet: Zaza Pachulia played for the Magic in 2003-04, the Bucks in 2004-05, the Hawks from 2005-06 to 2012-13, the Bucks from 2013-14 to 2014-15, the Mavericks in 2015-16, the Warriors from 2016-17 to 2017-18 and the Pistons in 2018-19.
